{
  "id": "adv_card_yu_07_03",
  "title": "鈴村優 3話 午後は独り占め",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "ほな、午後は{user}さんを\nうちがずーっと、独り占めしてもええんちゃう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ in the afternoon‚\nisn't it only fair that I get to have you all to myself?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "今から二人きりで抜け出しましょ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let’s sneak out and be alone together starting now!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 11.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "俺を独り占めって……それに、今から！？\nまだグラビア撮影は終わってないんだが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alone with me… and right now!?\nThe photo shoot isn’t over yet…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "機材の調整に、もう少しかかりそうやし\n終わったらスマホに連絡もらえばいいやんか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Adjustments to the equipment will take a little longer.\nJust let me know on my phone when it's done.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.857846419,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 26.0911797523
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃんとすみれちゃんとは遊びに行ったのに\nなんで、うちだけあかんの……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You went out and had fun with Rui-chan and Sumire-chan.\nSo why can’t I have fun too…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.457846419,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "い、いや、優と一緒が嫌な訳じゃなくて……\n分かった、撮影再開するまで少しだけだぞ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s not that I don’t want to be with Yu…\nAlright‚ just a little before the shoot resumes.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 42.6958735783
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "わ～、アイスクリーム、いろんな味がありますね\n{user}さんは何味にします？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow‚ there are so many flavors of ice cream.\nWhat flavor are you going to have‚ {user}-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.662540245,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-coast-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 43.3333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "あ、この味美味しそうやね。これ、一つください\nふふ、こういうとこでアイス食べるんは久しぶりやわ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ this one looks delicious. I’ll have one of these.\nHehe‚ it’s been a while since I had ice cream in a place like this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.662540245,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 62.8625354131
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "……アイス食べるだけで、本当に良かったのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Is just eating ice cream really enough?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.8625354131,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "あんなに遊びに行きたがってたから\nてっきり海で泳ぐとか、買い物しまくるのかと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You seemed so eager to go out and play.\nI thought for sure you’d want to swim at the beach or go shopping a lot…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.9239117927,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 72.898181804
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ。どんな無茶を言われるか\n気が気じゃなかった、って顔やね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe. You look like you’re worried about\nwhat crazy thing I might say.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.1315199692,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "うちだって、今が撮影中なのは分かってます\nいつ呼ばれるか分からんし、今はこれで我慢します",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand that we’re in the middle of a shoot.\nI don’t know when I’ll be called‚ so I’ll have to make do with this for now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.0315199692,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 87.198181804
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ、もし今日が丸ごとオフやったら……\n{user}さんをまず新幹線に乗せて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ if today had been a full day off…\nI’d first put {user}-san on the bullet train…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.7981866359,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（一体、俺に何をやらせるつもりだったんだろう……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（What on earth was she planning to make me do…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.6648484707,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 97.9596104622
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "今日は悪かったよ\nお詫びに、そのアイスは俺がおごるから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m sorry for today.\nTo make up for it‚ this ice cream is on me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 102.3455968857
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03-yu010.m4a",
      "text": "呆れた。あんな必死にうちの機嫌をとってたのに\nアイス代、うちに払わせるつもりやったんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m amazed. After trying so hard to cheer me up‚\nyou were planning to make me pay for the ice cream‚ weren’t you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.1789350509,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "ご、誤解だ！　もちろん最初からそんなつもりは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "N-no‚ it’s a misunderstanding! Of course‚ that wasn’t my intention from the start…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.1122635524,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 115.3857135456
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03-yu011.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、分かってますって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe‚ I know.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.3857135456,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03-yu012.m4a",
      "text": "ところで{user}さん、気付いてました？\nうちの衣装だけ、ほら、ちょ～っと濡れてるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By the way‚ {user}-san‚ did you notice?\nMy outfit is‚ see‚ just a little wet.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.7857183774,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03-yu013.m4a",
      "text": "テストの時に、偉いカメラマンさんが\n少し濡れた方が色っぽいね～なんて言うたから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The famous photographer said it looked more sensual\nif it was a little wet during the test.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.1322398754,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、その話をしてるのは俺も聞いてたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ I heard that too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.5190346719,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03-yu014.m4a",
      "text": "聞いてたなら、褒めてくれてもええやないですか\nどうです？　うち、ちゃんと色っぽく見えますか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you heard it‚ you could have complimented me.\nSo‚ what do you think? Do I look sensual?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、夏っぽくて可愛いと思うぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ it looks cute and summery to me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.7242189885,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03-yu015.m4a",
      "text": "もう。それじゃ答えになってません\nうちは色っぽいかどうか聞いてるんです～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmph. That doesn’t really answer my question.\nI’m asking if I look sensual or not~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.5412730694,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "そういうのはあまりおおっぴらに言うもんじゃ……\n……い、色っぽく見えるし、よく似合ってるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ such things aren’t usually said out loud…\n…Y-you do look sensual‚ and it suits you well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 164.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03-yu016.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、合格とはいきませんけど\n{user}さんにしては上出来やね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe‚ it’s not quite a pass‚\nbut it’s quite good for {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 173.075072209,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "あ、スタッフさんからスマホに連絡が\nそろそろ撮影再開するみたいだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ I got a message from the staff on my phone.\nLooks like the shoot will resume soon.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 179.5333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
